596f6c31-2721-9bc1-39ba-7d3a82f2887a.description	"<p>Two bulls were grazing at the bottom of the big pasture, when the farmer let a load of heifers in at the top gate.</p>\n<p>&#8220;Hey,&#8221; said the young bull to the old, &#8220;What do you say we run up there and fuck us a couple of heifers?&#8221;</p>\n<p>&#8220;Well,&#8221; said the old one, &#8220;You&#8217;re welcome to do that if you want to, but I plan on walking up there and fucking all of them&#8221;.</p>\n<p>I&#8217;ll leave any interpretation up to you.</p>"
