256f62cd-bbe6-afb9-c259-a00a027ac37e.title	"Trying to have it all: Acer's Timeline M5 gaming Ultrabook"
256f62cd-bbe6-afb9-c259-a00a027ac37e.author	"Andrew Cunningham"
256f62cd-bbe6-afb9-c259-a00a027ac37e.categories	["Features","Gear & Gadgets","Opposable Thumbs","Acer","gaming","ultrabook","windows 8"]
