23c1623f-8306-f0d7-edc6-0843b14d4105.title	"Unprefixed CSS3 Gradients in IE10"
23c1623f-8306-f0d7-edc6-0843b14d4105.author	"ieblog"
23c1623f-8306-f0d7-edc6-0843b14d4105.categories	["Developers","CSS","New in IE10"]
