8c6e5505-7562-269c-05d6-acb560eda0ab.title	"Windows Release Preview: The Sixth IE10 Platform Preview"
8c6e5505-7562-269c-05d6-acb560eda0ab.author	"ieblog"
8c6e5505-7562-269c-05d6-acb560eda0ab.categories	["Platform Preview","New in IE10"]
