4ad7d0c0-a1f3-1138-2fb4-f22a149f44c9.title	"High Quality Visuals for Pinned Sites in Windows 8"
4ad7d0c0-a1f3-1138-2fb4-f22a149f44c9.author	"ieblog"
4ad7d0c0-a1f3-1138-2fb4-f22a149f44c9.categories	["Developers","User Experiences","New in IE10"]
